html(lang="en")
    head
        title File Metadata Microservice
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    
    body
        div(class="container")
            h1(class="header") File Metadata Microservice
            br 

            blockquote
                User stories:
                ul
                    li 1) I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload
                    li 2) When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response
            br

            blockquote
                p Submit a file to view its filesize.
                form( method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action=basePath+"/upload")
                    input(name="file" type="file")
                    input(type="Submit")
            div
                br
                a(href=baseUrl) More freeCodeCamp apps